<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>SevMerge - IT 외주 입찰 플랫폼</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; background: #f5f6fa; color: #1c1e26; line-height: 1.6; }
    a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; }

    /* ── 버튼 ── */
    .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 22px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; border: none; font-family: inherit; transition: all .15s; }
    .btn-primary { background: #2563eb; color: #fff; }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: #1d4ed8; }
    .btn-outline { background: #fff; border: 1.5px solid #e2e5ef; color: #4b5563; }
    .btn-outline:hover { border-color: #2563eb; color: #2563eb; }
    .btn-lg { padding: 14px 32px; font-size: 15px; border-radius: 10px; }

    /* ── NAV ── */
    .nav { background: #fff; border-bottom: 1px solid #eaecf4; position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100; }
    .nav-inner { max-width: 1140px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 28px; height: 64px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 32px; }
    .nav-logo { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 900; color: #1c1e26; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
    .nav-logo span { color: #2563eb; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; font-weight: 500; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: #1c1e26; }
    .nav-actions { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
    .nav-username { font-size: 13px; color: #9ca3af; font-weight: 500; margin-right: 4px; }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .hero { background: #fff; border-bottom: 1px solid #eaecf4; padding: 88px 28px 76px; }
    .hero-inner { max-width: 1140px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 72px; align-items: center; }
    .hero-eyebrow { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: #2563eb; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .hero-eyebrow::before { content: ''; width: 20px; height: 2px; background: #2563eb; border-radius: 2px; }
    .hero-title { font-size: 50px; font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.12; letter-spacing: -2px; color: #1c1e26; margin-bottom: 18px; }
    .hero-title em { color: #2563eb; font-style: normal; }
    .hero-desc { font-size: 15px; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 36px; font-weight: 400; }
    .hero-btns { display: flex; gap: 12px; }
    .hero-trust { display: flex; gap: 20px; margin-top: 28px; }
    .trust-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-size: 13px; color: #9ca3af; font-weight: 500; }
    .trust-dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: #2563eb; }

    /* 히어로 우측 패널 */
    .hero-panel { background: #f8f9ff; border: 1px solid #e2e8ff; border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; }
    .hero-panel-header { padding: 18px 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e8ecf8; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; background: #fff; }
    .hero-panel-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #374151; }
    .live-badge { font-size: 11px; background: #eff6ff; color: #2563eb; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 20px; font-weight: 700; border: 1px solid #bfdbfe; }
    .stat-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); background: #fff; border-bottom: 1px solid #e8ecf8; }
    .stat-item { padding: 20px 12px; text-align: center; border-right: 1px solid #e8ecf8; }
    .stat-item:last-child { border-right: none; }
    .stat-val { display: block; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 900; color: #2563eb; margin-bottom: 4px; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
    .stat-lbl { font-size: 11px; color: #9ca3af; font-weight: 500; }
    .bid-preview { padding: 4px 24px 8px; }
    .bid-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 13px; padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f2f9; }
    .bid-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .bid-avatar { width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 12px; background: #eff6ff; border: 1px solid #bfdbfe; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 18px; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .bid-info { flex: 1; }
    .bid-name { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #1c1e26; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px; margin-bottom: 2px; }
    .cert-badge { font-size: 10px; background: #fffbeb; color: #b45309; border: 1px solid #fde68a; padding: 1px 7px; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: 700; }
    .bid-spec { font-size: 11px; color: #9ca3af; font-weight: 400; }
    .bid-price { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 900; color: #2563eb; letter-spacing: -0.3px; }

    /* ── SEARCH ── */
    .search-section { background: #fff; border-bottom: 1px solid #eaecf4; padding: 32px 28px 36px; }
    .search-inner { max-width: 1140px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }
    .search-bar { display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .search-input { flex: 1; padding: 13px 18px; background: #f8f9fc; border: 1.5px solid #e2e5ef; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 14px; font-family: inherit; color: #1c1e26; outline: none; transition: border-color .15s; font-weight: 400; }
    .search-input::placeholder { color: #c4c9d9; }
    .search-input:focus { border-color: #2563eb; background: #fff; }
    .search-btn { padding: 13px 28px; background: #2563eb; color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit; }
    .search-btn:hover { background: #1d4ed8; }
    .category-tabs { display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .tab { padding: 8px 18px; border-radius: 20px; border: 1.5px solid #e2e5ef; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; background: #fff; transition: all .15s; }
    .tab:hover { border-color: #2563eb; color: #2563eb; }
    .tab.active { background: #2563eb; border-color: #2563eb; color: #fff; }
    .tab-certified { border-color: #fde68a; color: #b45309; background: #fffdf5; }
    .tab-certified:hover { border-color: #f59e0b; color: #92400e; background: #fffbeb; }

    /* ── PROJECT LIST ── */
    .project-section { padding: 52px 28px 80px; }
    .project-inner { max-width: 1140px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .section-head { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .section-title { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 900; color: #1c1e26; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
    .view-all { font-size: 13px; color: #2563eb; font-weight: 600; }
    .view-all:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    .project-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 18px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
    .project-card { background: #fff; border: 1.5px solid #eaecf4; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; transition: border-color .2s, box-shadow .2s, transform .15s; }
    .project-card:hover { border-color: #bfdbfe; box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(37,99,235,.08); transform: translateY(-3px); }
    .project-card-link { display: block; padding: 24px; }
    .project-card-top { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .project-category { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; color: #2563eb; background: #eff6ff; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 6px; letter-spacing: .3px; }
    .badge-certified { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; color: #b45309; background: #fffbeb; border: 1px solid #fde68a; padding: 3px 9px; border-radius: 6px; }
    .project-title { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: #1c1e26; margin-bottom: 8px; line-height: 1.5; }
    .project-desc { font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: 400; }
    .project-card-bottom { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; border-top: 1px solid #f3f4f8; padding-top: 14px; }
    .project-budget { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 900; color: #1c1e26; letter-spacing: -0.3px; }
    .project-meta { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-size: 12px; color: #c4c9d9; font-weight: 600; }
    .d-day { color: #c4c9d9; }
    .d-day.urgent { color: #ef4444; font-weight: 700; }

    /* ── EMPTY ── */
    .empty-state { text-align: center; padding: 80px 0; }
    .empty-msg { font-size: 15px; color: #c4c9d9; margin-bottom: 20px; }

    /* ── PAGING ── */
    .paging { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 6px; }
    .page-btn { padding: 9px 15px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1.5px solid #e2e5ef; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; background: #fff; transition: all .15s; }
    .page-btn:hover { border-color: #2563eb; color: #2563eb; }
    .page-btn.active { background: #2563eb; border-color: #2563eb; color: #fff; }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    .footer { background: #fff; border-top: 1px solid #eaecf4; padding: 36px 28px; }
    .footer-inner { max-width: 1140px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 16px; }
    .footer-logo { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 900; color: #1c1e26; }
    .footer-logo span { color: #2563eb; }
    .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 24px; font-size: 13px; color: #9ca3af; font-weight: 500; }
    .footer-links a:hover { color: #1c1e26; }
    .footer-copy { font-size: 12px; color: #c4c9d9; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<header class="nav">
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a href="/" class="nav-logo">Sev<span>Merge</span></a>
    <nav class="nav-links">
      <a href="/projects">프로젝트</a>
      <a href="/experts">전문가</a>
      <a href="/boards">커뮤니티</a>
      <a href="/mypage">마이페이지</a>
    </nav>
    <div class="nav-actions">
      <span class="nav-username">홍길동님</span>
      <a href="/auth/logout" class="btn btn-outline">로그아웃</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow">역제안 입찰 플랫폼</div>
      <h1 class="hero-title">전문가가<br />직접 찾아오는<br /><em>IT 외주</em></h1>
      <p class="hero-desc">
        프로젝트를 등록하면 검증된 전문가들이<br />
        제안서를 보내드립니다. 인증 뱃지, 에스크로 결제,<br />
        실시간 채팅으로 안전하게 시작하세요.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-btns">
        <a href="/projects/save-form" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">프로젝트 무료 등록</a>
        <a href="/experts" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">전문가 둘러보기</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-trust">
        <span class="trust-item"><span class="trust-dot"></span>검증된 전문가</span>
        <span class="trust-item"><span class="trust-dot"></span>에스크로 결제</span>
        <span class="trust-item"><span class="trust-dot"></span>실시간 채팅</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-panel">
      <div class="hero-panel-header">
        <span class="hero-panel-title">실시간 입찰 현황</span>
        <span class="live-badge">LIVE</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-row">
        <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-val">1,240</span><span class="stat-lbl">등록 전문가</span></div>
        <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-val">843</span><span class="stat-lbl">완료 프로젝트</span></div>
        <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-val">4.8★</span><span class="stat-lbl">평균 만족도</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="bid-preview">
        <div class="bid-item">
          <div class="bid-avatar">👨‍💻</div>
          <div class="bid-info">
            <div class="bid-name">김개발 <span class="cert-badge">⭐ 인증</span></div>
            <div class="bid-spec">풀스택 · Spring Boot · 5년</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bid-price">180만원</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bid-item">
          <div class="bid-avatar">👩‍💻</div>
          <div class="bid-info">
            <div class="bid-name">이백엔드 <span class="cert-badge">⭐ 인증</span></div>
            <div class="bid-spec">백엔드 · Java · 4년</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bid-price">200만원</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bid-item">
          <div class="bid-avatar">👨‍🎨</div>
          <div class="bid-info">
            <div class="bid-name">박프론트</div>
            <div class="bid-spec">프론트엔드 · React · 3년</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bid-price">155만원</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SEARCH + FILTER -->
<section class="search-section">
  <div class="search-inner">
    <form class="search-form" action="/projects" method="GET">
      <div class="search-bar">
        <input type="text" name="keyword" placeholder="프로젝트 키워드로 검색해보세요..." value="" class="search-input" />
        <button type="submit" class="search-btn">검색</button>
      </div>
      <div class="category-tabs">
        <a href="/projects" class="tab active">전체</a>
        <a href="/projects?category=WEB" class="tab">웹개발</a>
        <a href="/projects?category=APP" class="tab">앱개발</a>
        <a href="/projects?category=UIUX" class="tab">UI/UX</a>
        <a href="/projects?category=DATA" class="tab">데이터</a>
        <a href="/projects?category=VIDEO" class="tab">영상편집</a>
        <a href="/projects?category=ETC" class="tab">기타</a>
        <a href="/projects?bidFilter=CERTIFIED_ONLY" class="tab tab-certified">⭐ 인증 전문가만</a>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PROJECT LIST -->
<section class="project-section">
  <div class="project-inner">

    <div class="section-head">
      <h2 class="section-title">등록된 프로젝트</h2>
      <a href="/projects" class="view-all">전체보기 →</a>
    </div>

    <div class="project-grid">

      <article class="project-card">
        <a href="/projects/1" class="project-card-link">
          <div class="project-card-top">
            <span class="project-category">웹개발</span>
            <span class="badge-certified">⭐ 인증 전문가만</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="project-title">쇼핑몰 백오피스 관리자 시스템 구축</h3>
          <p class="project-desc">Spring Boot 기반 관리자 대시보드, 상품/주문/회원 관리 기능 개발</p>
          <div class="project-card-bottom">
            <div class="project-budget">150~200만원</div>
            <div class="project-meta">
              <span class="bid-count">입찰 7개</span>
              <span class="d-day urgent">D-3</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </article>

      <article class="project-card">
        <a href="/projects/2" class="project-card-link">
          <div class="project-card-top">
            <span class="project-category">앱개발</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="project-title">헬스케어 앱 React Native 개발</h3>
          <p class="project-desc">운동 기록, 식단 관리, 소셜 기능 포함한 iOS/Android 앱 개발</p>
          <div class="project-card-bottom">
            <div class="project-budget">500~700만원</div>
            <div class="project-meta">
              <span class="bid-count">입찰 12개</span>
              <span class="d-day">D-7</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </article>

      <article class="project-card">
        <a href="/projects/3" class="project-card-link">
          <div class="project-card-top">
            <span class="project-category">UI/UX</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="project-title">B2B SaaS 대시보드 디자인 시스템 구축</h3>
          <p class="project-desc">Figma 기반 디자인 시스템, 반응형 UI/UX 설계 및 프로토타입 제작</p>
          <div class="project-card-bottom">
            <div class="project-budget">협의 가능</div>
            <div class="project-meta">
              <span class="bid-count">입찰 5개</span>
              <span class="d-day">D-10</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </article>

      <article class="project-card">
        <a href="/projects/4" class="project-card-link">
          <div class="project-card-top">
            <span class="project-category">데이터</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="project-title">AI 기반 상품 추천 알고리즘 개발</h3>
          <p class="project-desc">Python, PyTorch 기반 협업 필터링 추천 시스템 구축 및 API 연동</p>
          <div class="project-card-bottom">
            <div class="project-budget">300~500만원</div>
            <div class="project-meta">
              <span class="bid-count">입찰 9개</span>
              <span class="d-day">D-5</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </article>

      <article class="project-card">
        <a href="/projects/5" class="project-card-link">
          <div class="project-card-top">
            <span class="project-category">웹개발</span>
            <span class="badge-certified">⭐ 인증 전문가만</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="project-title">실시간 경매 플랫폼 웹 서비스 개발</h3>
          <p class="project-desc">WebSocket 기반 실시간 입찰 시스템, 결제 연동, 어드민 포함</p>
          <div class="project-card-bottom">
            <div class="project-budget">400~600만원</div>
            <div class="project-meta">
              <span class="bid-count">입찰 3개</span>
              <span class="d-day urgent">D-1</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </article>

      <article class="project-card">
        <a href="/projects/6" class="project-card-link">
          <div class="project-card-top">
            <span class="project-category">앱개발</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="project-title">부동산 매물 검색 앱 Flutter 개발</h3>
          <p class="project-desc">지도 API 연동, 필터 검색, 찜 기능, 푸시 알림 포함한 앱 전체 개발</p>
          <div class="project-card-bottom">
            <div class="project-budget">350~500만원</div>
            <div class="project-meta">
              <span class="bid-count">입찰 6개</span>
              <span class="d-day">D-14</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </article>

    </div>

    <div class="paging">
      <a href="/projects?page=1" class="page-btn active">1</a>
      <a href="/projects?page=2" class="page-btn">2</a>
      <a href="/projects?page=3" class="page-btn">3</a>
      <a href="/projects?page=2" class="page-btn">다음</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<footer class="footer">
  <div class="footer-inner">
    <span class="footer-logo">Sev<span>Merge</span></span>
    <div class="footer-links">
      <a href="/boards?type=NOTICE">공지사항</a>
      <a href="/boards?type=INQUIRY">1:1 문의</a>
    </div>
    <p class="footer-copy">&copy; 2025 SevMerge. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
